OWLTableModel, SymbolTableModel, Serializable, TableModel
public class PropertiesSuperclassesTableModel
extends AbstractOWLTableModel

A ClassDescriptionTableModel that displays all direct superclasses that are not restrictions. This implementation assumes that the edited class has no equivalent classes.

Author:
Holger Knublauch
